moviedirbrowser (mdb)
###############

A program that shows information relating to the selected movie file/folder
from IMDB.

DBbuilder
---------
- For file names passed
	- Parses movie name from filename
	- Searches on imdb, copies image to .mdb folder, info to db
	- Signals GUI

GUI
---
- wxpython
- shows 1 movie or more

Working
-------
- GUI is passed 1 or more filenames
	- if filename found in db its drawn
	- else all the not-found ones are collected and dbbuilder is launched on them
		- GUI is updated as each movie becomes available

Future
--------
- Windows support no
- Use opensubs database in addition to file name
- Option to download subs
- Release on github pages
- Cache the GUI output
